::Zardus::

"Excellent," Zardus replies, truly relieved. This was going 
well, "Some aireal bots of mine are attacking Hell Beast's base. If 
you have any bots that can fly, they could help mine out there. If 
you want, the land bots can go to the Cybertronian Fire to attack 
Hell BEast's troops there. I have a possible mutiny in my base right 
now, so I can't send too many troops."
